0: ”Alexa, open Dive into the World of Trivia.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: dive into the world of trivia
des: This game is for all those who want to test their skills in a variety of subjects including General Knowledge, Technology, History, Geography and many more. Challenge your friends and family and make your own high score. This trivia game will ask you twenty questions. Try to get as many correct answers as possible. This game's much fun. Let's Dive into the World of Trivia.
